name: Comic Cover
description: This is a model that's based on the style of comic cover some common things it does are logos bar codes and titles. Tends to work best at 0.6. This model was trained on NAI anime-full-pruned and generated in AOM3. Made with the Kohya tool for AI Training through google colab. Any suggestions to improve or recommended things for the data set would be appreciated.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description:
